items.title: These drone motors can carry a car!
items.author: Strange Parts
items.summary:
- In Donguan, China, a journey through the production of *giant drone motors* begins at the magnet factory, where specialized processes transform raw neodymium into powerful magnets. 
- The stator factory employs *precision stamping* techniques to create components essential for motor efficiency, showcasing advanced manufacturing tools. 
- Significant steps like winding and inspection illustrate the meticulous craftsmanship behind creating motors capable of lifting heavy loads, including vehicles.
